                        "**amount**: The scheduled transaction amount in milliunits format",
                        "**category_id**",
                        "**date_first**: The first date for which the Scheduled Transaction was scheduled.",
                        "**date_next**: The next date for which the Scheduled Transaction is scheduled.",
                        "**deleted**: Whether or not the scheduled transaction has been deleted.  Deleted scheduled transactions will only be included in delta requests.",
                        "**flag_color**: The scheduled transaction flag",
                        "**frequency**",
                        "**id**",
                        "**memo**",
                        "**payee_id**",
                        "**transfer_account_id**: If a transfer, the account_id which the scheduled transaction transfers to",
                        "**account_name**",
                        "**category_name**: The name of the category.  If a split scheduled transaction, this will be 'Split'.",
                        "**payee_name**",
                        "**subtransactions**: If a split scheduled transaction, the subtransactions."
